sources.title: West of Pinto Basin (1940) THE RANGE BUSTERS
sources.description:
First Time on YouTube!
Stars: Ray Corrigan, John 'Dusty' King, Max Terhune
Director: S. Roy Luby

The Range Busters battle a saloon owner who is trying to grab up all the local land by engineering stagecoach robberies so an irrigation dam can't be built.

metadata.Plot: The Range Busters head for Pinto Basin where a series of stage robberies have occurred. To try and find the gang's boss, Crash sends out a empty money box. The plan backfires when the boss has the Range Busters identified as the robbers. Thinking it is now safe, the bank sends out a big money shipment. Needing to rob the stage, the boss gets the boys out of jail so they can be blamed. But this is just the chance they need to catch the robbers.
metadata.Actors: Ray Corrigan, John 'Dusty' King, Max Terhune
